@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Add Transaction
actor User
participant "UI (Form)" as UI
participant "React App" as App
participant "AppContext" as Context
participant "Local Storage" as Local

User -> UI: Open New Transaction Form
UI -> User: Show Form
User -> UI: Submit Transaction Data
UI -> App: dispatch(addTransaction)
App -> Context: addTransaction(payload)
Context -> Local: saveTransaction(transaction)
Local --> Context: success
Context --> App: state updated
App --> UI: show confirmation
@enduml